Name: CiscoDuoSecurity
Author: Mallikarjun Udanashiv - v-maudan@microsoft.com
Description: [Duo](https://duo.com/product) is the user-friendly zero-trust security platform for all users, all devices and all applications.Cisco and Duo are closely aligned in the approach of designing infrastructure for the extended enterprise where users, devices and applications are the center of the modern security architecture.
